\section*{Assignment 1: Intro}

\textbf{Part 1 (75 points):} Describe your favorite WebGL demo.

\vspace{.5cm} % add some space

\noindent My favorite demo is Earth 2050 human civilization prediction. It is well organized,detailed ,and most interactive as well informative. Here is the link (\url{https://2050.earth}). It is built by Kaspersky organization, a representation of actual data with optimistic approach. Great tool to look in to the future,I get immersed of course it looks realistic.

